LongDescription:
The Irsavatha class cruisers are the most modern and advanced ships within the Falcatan navy, having entered service only five years ago. They are fast, reasonably maneuverable, and pack a powerful punch. This package is additionally sweetened by the classes advanced EWAR capabilities.

Suitable for use independently or in a group, the Irsavatha can be expected to handily defeat peer opponents, while retaining enough speed to flee from anything larger.
